eqh3Xtw8jWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=d296bb68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Fortune.Pharmacal/</a><br />\n2015 『獅子山精神』<br />\n2018 『本地薑可以強』<br />\n2011 『幸福要走多步』<br />\n<br />\n維他奶 fb follower: 89k <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vitavitasoy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvitavitasoy%2F&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw8jWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=4b412edb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vitavitasoy/</a><br />\n2009 2015 『Stand by me』<br />\n<br />\n富衛保險 fb follower: 38k <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FWD.HK.MO/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFWD.HK.MO%2F&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw8jWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=cd9d20dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FWD.HK.MO/</a><br />\n2014『敢至係人生』<br />\n2019 『豁出去向前行我哋支持你』<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以一齊發聲俾企業知道佢哋消費過本土情懷，就有責任喺香港存亡關頭出力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係洗版懶人template keypoints 建議大家加以自行發揮,動之以情曉之以理： <br />\n1。提及佢哋曾經用過嘅tagline，創造過香港人嘅集體回憶<br />\n2。作為香港人, 我哋對有良心，敢作敢為嘅企業感到驕傲，亦會用消費選擇回報呢種公司<br />\n3。69遊行人數103萬， 近人口15% 。以真香港人為目標市場嘅貴企業希望可以同顧客站喺同一陣線, 再更進一步取得呢一批人嘅支持<br />\n<br />\n同時 希望巴絲brainstorm 多d 其他同類brand, 集思廣益， 擴大個list 佢。各大100毛廣告客戶會有potential，我哋需要啲肯變通嘅企業加入反抗大軍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85f097bd248e586207c485edaffca01bbd3b482","tid":1199255,"uid":109647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07973f4ac12d24e2d0fea6c93ad2c359d1b05f58","tid":1199255,"uid":109647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:26:41.000Z","msg":"在外國或有包袱唔能夠同義士一齊衝嘅巴絲打，都想四大地產商會做嘢，但係確實係難過登天。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse